{
  "stem": "4284.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The working conditions in Auschwitz on this animal farm, if you can call it, provided us also with the additional, I can't say freedom, but opportunity to move about.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were on this farm-like setting on these stables, that we were not in the camp to be selected or to be necessarily cruelly treated if and when the Germans decided to do something for their amusement, or to clean out, or select people for extermination, which was very frequently done due to the fact that everybody suffered from enormous malnutrition.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And many people rapidly were declining.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as soon as you got too weak to do any other kind of work, you were gone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when we came back at night, we had to be accounted for.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so at 6 o'clock every night, we had a head count.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, my job, along with some others, was also to take the horses to be fed, not in the stable but on the fields.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to do field work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to do some plowing as long as our horses could do-- many different things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The one time I almost came to a bitter end was that I was taking this one horse, which was supposed to be ready for delivery of it's foal.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the Germans decided the horse needed the best nutrition.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm supposed to take it to a clover field where the horse could eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, the horse decided at about five minutes to 6:00 to have its baby.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it laid down and proceeded to give birth just behind a bulge in, in the field.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
